description: XANO Industri AB engages in the development, acquisition, and operation of manufacturing businesses and systems. The company is headquartered in Jonkoping, Jonkopings and currently employs 1,125 full-time employees.  The company acquires and operates companies providing manufacturing and development services for industrial products and automation equipment. The firm's subsidiaries are grouped into three business units. The Industrial Products unit designs, manufactures and markets plastic components and systems produced using such technologies as rotational molding, injection molding and blow molding. The Industrial Solutions unit develops automation solutions for the packaging industry, including packaging machines, accumulators and conveyor systems. The Precision Technology unit manufactures components and systems through cutting-machining of metal and plastic. The firm operates in the Nordic countries, Estonia, the Netherlands, Poland, China and the United States, among others.
name: XANO Industri AB
